		<Desc>多情天尊张煜承曾将自身七情尽数炼入此剑，不仅威力绝伦，执剑者也会从当中领悟出剑道真意，突破御剑极限10级。然多情伤人伤己，会对执剑者的心情与心境造成影响。</Desc>
		<MaxStack>1</MaxStack>
		<Duration>-1</Duration>
		<Display>1</Display>
		<Properties>

			<li Name="NpcFight_FabaoPowerAddP" AddP="500"/>
			
			
			
			<li Name="NightmareHappenPercent" AddP="0.2"/>
			<li Name="SpeedOfMindStateCoefficient" AddP="-5"/>
			
			<li Name="BaseEmotionAddV" AddV="-30"/>
			<li Name="MindStateBaseValue" AddV="-30"/>
		</Properties>

		<Skills>
			<li Name="Fabao" LevelOver="10"/>
		</Skills>
	</Modifier>

