		<DisplayName>华杰之主</DisplayName>
		<Desc>拥有㱾鋆御哨之人将被华杰之野的黎民奉为天皇，受万千百姓爱戴，突破护体极限20级。</Desc>
		<MaxStack>1</MaxStack>
		<Duration>-1</Duration>
		<Display>1</Display>

		<Skills>
			<li Name="Barrier" Level="40"/>
			<li Name="Barrier" LevelOver="20"/>
		</Skills>
	</Modifier>

	<Modifier Name="万念" Type="Normal">
		<DisplayName>万念</DisplayName>
		<Desc>万念剑中蕴含着多情天尊对于故人的万千念想，将大幅度影响执剑者心境，且噩梦连连。</Desc>
		<MaxStack>1</MaxStack>
		<Duration>-1</Duration>
		<Display>1</Display>

		<Properties>
			
			<li Name="NightmareHappenPercent" AddP="0.5"/>
			
